
At Iznassen llan yiwen n teqbilin i yellan deg tama tanegmuḍant n Merruk tama n tilas n Dzayer. Xas At Iznassen laṣel-nsen d Amaziɣ, tigti deg-sen ur ittmeslayen ara tamaziɣt ass-a acuk mazal (ursul) llan imdanen i yimelsayen-itt mliḥ imir-a. 

==Usunen (lɛerc)==


* '''At Xaled''' di tama n Aḥfir ar Fezwan. Deg wakal n At Xaled, At Mrin bnan leqṣar d ameẓyan, bnan yiwet "teqṣebt" ɣef ayed ad nezmer ad neẓra igulaz-is acku medden nfan-itt am yella akka. 

* '''At Menquc''' si Reggada ar Labsara di wenẓul, si Fezwan ar asif n "Caraɛa" i yezgran tamdint n Aberkan. Akalen n At Menquc tella daɣen di temdint n Aberkan. 

* '''At Ɛaṭiq''' i d-yezgan gar Asif n Caraɛa ar Rislan d Tafuɣalt d Zegzel (Zeyzel s tmaziɣt-nsen). 

* '''At Waryemmec''', wigi d Iznassen i yellan qrib n tamwyaya n At Bu Yeḥyi d temwaya n At Seṭṭut n temnaṭ n Nnadur. Tamaneɣt n At Bu Yeḥyi d "Ḥassi Berkan" daɣ "Lɛarwi" af webrid gar Nnadur d Tewrirt, tamaneɣt n At Seṭṭut d Zayyu. 


